snippet.description:
Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
Mario Maker's Pumpkin Head Challenge ►► http://bit.ly/1khg2o7
The Impossible Quiz: The Fail Begins! ►► http://bit.ly/1PqHnPO

What do you do when you are called in to disarm a bomb that you know nothing about? Call in some friends who know just as little. The Warp Zone joins me in playing one of the most stressful games I've ever played. But it is also one of the most fun group games I've played as well. Let's see if we can keep everyone safe, and entertained. It is really a lot of pressure!

Check Out The Warp Zone ►►
